{
  "stem": "11552.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then they gave me something for lunch, and then whatever, if they had a piece of bread leftover, or potatoes, I took them to my mother.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then another woman came with her two daughters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then one day, I was working in the field.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were harvesting potatoes, and that was 1943.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I overheard somebody-- two Ukrainian young boys were working there-- they said-- they were laughing because they are going to-- they found this-- this Jews in-- in the fields, and they're-- they're going to kill them.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Actually, it-- well, no, we weren't harvesting [? potato ?]-- we were weeding potatoes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We were taking the weeds out, so it was like in middle of the summer, before harvest.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'43.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they say that they-- that they were in-- in-- in that wheat field, and that they are going to let the Ukrainian police know about them, that they're going to kill them.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were laughing and things like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were saying, the wheat field near the mill, there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So, but, you know, there are many wheat fields.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I realized, they are going to be killed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the only way I can do is try to find them before they are found and trying to rescue them and take them to safety.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Can you imagine, my trying to find that-- that field?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when people were hiding, the-- the wheat in Poland is very tall, and when you go into the field, you make tracks because you have to separate the stalks.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they stay separated because people don't really know how to walk on the field.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so finally, I found that area that was damaged in the stalks, and I tracked them down.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
